Manage Users Guide
1
Open your browser and navigate to: "https://IP_Data_Collector/". You can also use
the a4conf icon on the Data Collector desktop.
2
Click "Manage-Users" within the main menu.
Made with Scribe - https://scribehow.com 2
3
Click the "Add" button to add a new user.
4
Enter the username in the "Username" field. It must be in email format.
Made with Scribe - https://scribehow.com 3
5
Enter the password in the "Password" filed. The password must be at least 8
characters long and contain one lower case letter, one upper case letter, one
number and one special character.
6
Confirm the password.
Made with Scribe - https://scribehow.com 4
7
Click the "eye" icon to see the password in cleartext.
8
Click the "Create" button.
Made with Scribe - https://scribehow.com 5
9
Click the "Delete" button to delete a user.
